('3abce753-64a5-4224-8a65-3038a62c0079', '7cdbaba4-eb3a-412f-a049-940993e1156b', '', 'Welcome to Your Signature Marketing Package', 'text', '<h2>You Just Made a Powerful Decision</h2><p><br></p><p>Welcome. I''m genuinely so excited you''re here.</p><p><br></p><p>You just made an investment in&nbsp;clarity, feedback, and real tools&nbsp;that are going to change how you approach growth. Not everyone takes this step—most people stay stuck in "I''ll figure it out later" mode forever. But you? You said yes. That''s huge.</p><p><br></p><p>This package isn''t just a folder of templates you''ll never use. It''s a&nbsp;complete system&nbsp;designed to take the overwhelm out of marketing and replace it with a plan you can actually execute.</p><p><br></p><p>Everything inside is customizable to&nbsp;<em>your</em>&nbsp;business,&nbsp;<em>your</em>&nbsp;audience, and&nbsp;<em>your</em>&nbsp;goals. No one-size-fits-all nonsense. Just real strategies that work.</p><p><br></p><p>Let''s get you oriented.</p><p><br></p><p>— <em>Kayla</em></p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:47:04.697Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:04.697Z'),
('93de3147-4375-44e2-b157-8ed357403725', '7cdbaba4-eb3a-412f-a049-940993e1156b', '', 'What You Just Got (The Full Breakdown)', 'text', '<h2>What You Just Got</h2><p><br></p><p>Here''s the honest truth: this package is&nbsp;a <strong>lot</strong>. And that''s on purpose.</p><p><br></p><p>I didn''t want to give you "just enough" to get started and then upsell you on the rest later. That''s not how I operate. You deserve everything upfront—the full toolkit, the strategies, the scripts, the templates—all of it.</p><p><br></p><p>But I also know that "everything" can feel overwhelming when you first log in. So let''s break it down.</p><p><br></p><h2>You now have access to:</h2><ul><li><strong>7 Complete Marketing Modules</strong>&nbsp;(YouTube, Instagram, Sponsorships, Partnerships, Affiliates, Branding, and Operations)</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>200+ Ready-to-Use Assets</strong>&nbsp;(calendars, scripts, templates, guides, email swipes, pitch decks, and more)</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>30-Day Implementation Plan</strong>&nbsp;(so you know exactly what to do first, second, and third)</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>Personal Strategy Support</strong>&nbsp;(because you''re not doing this alone)</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong>60-Day Access To Compass</strong> - Your Personal Social Media Tracker</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Everything is designed to work&nbsp;<em>for</em>&nbsp;you—not create more work. You customize what you need, skip what you don''t, and move forward with confidence.</p><p><br></p><h2>Here''s What''s Inside Each Module:</h2><p><strong>Module 1: YouTube Execution Assets</strong></p><p>Your long-game growth engine. 30-day calendar, ready-to-record scripts, SEO checklists, and analytics guides.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 2: Instagram Execution Assets</strong></p><p>The "anti-burnout" community builder. Posting calendars, carousel templates, engagement playbooks, and Reels strategies.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 3: Sponsorship &amp; Pitch Assets</strong></p><p>Turn influence into income. Outreach scripts, pitch decks, legal contracts, and pricing guides.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 4: Community &amp; Partnership Outreach</strong></p><p>The "Event-in-a-Box." Workshop outlines, cold email templates, and lead-capture strategies for offline growth.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 5: Affiliate Marketing System</strong></p><p>Build your sales force. Recruitment emails, onboarding packs, commission structures, and management tools.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 6: Branding &amp; Design Assets</strong></p><p>Look like a pro. Brand color palettes, Canva templates, social headers, and visual optimization checklists.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Module 7: Strategy &amp; Operations Hub</strong></p><p>Your CEO toolkit. 30-day timelines, decision frameworks, progress trackers, and troubleshooting guides.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">Bonus: Personal Consultation Access</strong></p><p><span style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">1:1 strategy calls and priority email support to help you execute with confidence.</span></p>', '', 2, '2025-12-28T19:47:04.435Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:04.435Z'),
('83b3e7b8-012d-4579-9d8e-174372abf57e', '7cdbaba4-eb3a-412f-a049-940993e1156b', '', 'Quick Video Walkthrough (Watch This First)', 'video', '', 'https://app.supademo.com/demo/cmjp3jtoa5yg13zz2eza2p0of?utm_source=link', 3, '2025-12-28T19:47:04.176Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:04.176Z'),
('0adee6e8-25fb-4b40-8c4b-c5cd3306a3fb', '7cdbaba4-eb3a-412f-a049-940993e1156b', '', 'Your Implementation Guide', 'text', '<h2>How to Use This Package</h2><p><br></p><h2>Step 1: Pick ONE Module to Start</h2><p>Don''t try to do everything. Choose based on your priority:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Need content ASAP?&nbsp;→ Module 1 (YouTube) or Module 2 (Instagram)</li><li><em>You''ll get 30-day calendars with topics, hooks, and captions ready to go.</em></li><li>Need revenue ASAP?&nbsp;→ Module 3 (Sponsorships) or Module 5 (Affiliates)</li><li><em>You''ll get outreach scripts, pitch templates, and legal agreements to start closing deals.</em></li><li>Need systems ASAP?&nbsp;→ Module 7 (Strategy &amp; Operations)</li><li><em>You''ll get your 30-day timeline, decision frameworks, and progress trackers.</em></li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Step 2: Follow the 30-Day Timeline (Module 7)</h2><p>Inside Module 7, you''ll find your&nbsp;30-Day Implementation Timeline. This is your day-by-day roadmap that tells you:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>What to prioritize first</li><li>What tasks to complete each week</li><li>How long each task should take</li><li>When to move to the next module</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Use it. It''s designed to prevent overwhelm and keep you moving forward.</p><p><br></p><h2>Step 3: Customize Every Template</h2><p>These aren''t "fill-in-the-blank" templates. They''re frameworks designed for&nbsp;<em>your</em>&nbsp;business.</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Replace placeholder text with your brand voice</li><li>Add your audience''s specific pain points</li><li>Adjust timelines and goals to match your capacity</li><li>Make it sound like YOU, not me</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Copy-paste won''t work. Customization will.</p><p><br></p><h2>Step 4: Execute, Then Reach Out</h2><p>Book your&nbsp;1:1 strategy call&nbsp;here:&nbsp;<a href="https://wix.to/NQrlG5I" target="_blank">https://wix.to/NQrlG5I</a></p><p><br></p><p>Use it to:</p><ul><li>Get unstuck on a specific challenge</li><li>Review your customized templates</li><li>Adjust your plan based on early results</li><li>Get feedback on content, pitches, or campaigns</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Email me&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:Kayla@KaylaSierra.com" target="_blank">Kayla@KaylaSierra.com</a> for quick questions (48-hour response time).</p><p><br></p><h2>What to Expect: First 30 Days</h2><p>Week 1:&nbsp;You''ll have clarity on your next steps and a clear plan.</p><p>Week 2:&nbsp;You''ll build momentum with consistent execution.</p><p>Week 3:&nbsp;You''ll see early results—engagement, responses, traction.</p><p>Week 4:&nbsp;You''ll have repeatable systems that scale.</p><p><br></p><p>The catch:&nbsp;You have to execute. I''m giving you the roadmap and tools. The work is on you.</p>', '', 4, '2025-12-28T19:47:03.917Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:03.917Z'),
('4efc9587-26b6-43d4-b876-fdd88e925574', '4e75ead9-b594-4b2e-ba69-775fd08c6977', '', 'YouTube Execution Assets Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 1: YouTube Execution Assets</h1><p>YouTube isn''t just another social platform—it''s a&nbsp;searchable asset library&nbsp;that works while you sleep. Every video you post can generate views, subscribers, and revenue for years.</p><p><br></p><p>This module removes the guesswork. You''ll get the exact content calendar, scripts, optimization strategies, and analytics frameworks to grow your channel without burning out.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>30-Day YouTube Posting Calendar&nbsp;– Day-by-day topics, hooks, and video ideas tailored to your niche. <a href="https://kaylasierra.com/compass" target="_blank"><strong>Log In to Compass Here to View.</strong></a><strong> New to Compass? Find your login credentials in your module. </strong></li><li><strong>3-5 Complete Video Scripts</strong>&nbsp;– Intro, body, and CTA ready to record </li><li><strong>20+ ChatGPT Prompts</strong>&nbsp;– Never run out of video ideas again</li><li><strong>YouTube Optimization Checklist</strong>&nbsp;– The exact formula for titles, descriptions, tags, and thumbnails</li><li><strong>Shorts Strategy Guide + 10 Clip Ideas</strong>&nbsp;– Repurpose long-form content into growth-driving Shorts - <strong>Contained in Compass. </strong></li><li><strong>YouTube Analytics Dashboard Guide</strong>&nbsp;– What metrics matter and how to read them</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You need a consistent content plan but don''t know what to post</li><li>You''re recording videos but getting low views because of poor SEO</li><li>You want to repurpose content into Shorts but don''t know where to start</li><li>You''re overwhelmed by analytics and don''t know what to track</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>30 days of content ready to execute</li><li>Scripts you can record immediately</li><li>A repeatable system for optimizing every upload</li><li>Clarity on which metrics drive growth</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;2-3 hours to review and customize. Then execute daily for 30 days.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:47:03.663Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:03.663Z'),
('4900e136-93ed-47bd-8049-af72828c81b1', '4e75ead9-b594-4b2e-ba69-775fd08c6977', '', 'Accessing Your 30-Day YouTube Calendar (Video Walkthrough)', 'video', '<p>Here''s how to access it:</p><p>Step 1:&nbsp;Log into Compass at http://kaylasierra.com/compass</p><p>Step 2:&nbsp;Navigate to ''Content Calendar'' in the left sidebar</p><p>Step 3:&nbsp;Filter by ''YouTube'' to see your 30-day plan</p>', 'https://app.supademo.com/demo/cmjp3jtoa5yg13zz2eza2p0of?utm_source=link', 2, '2025-12-28T19:47:03.418Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:03.418Z'),
('eec6b004-0118-4d95-bb64-09358a64bb98', '4e75ead9-b594-4b2e-ba69-775fd08c6977', '', 'Complete Video Scripts (Ready to Record)', 'embedded_file', '<p><strong>3-5 complete video scripts&nbsp;structured as:</strong></p><ul><li>Intro (Hook)&nbsp;– First 10 seconds to grab attention</li><li>Body (Value)&nbsp;– The teaching, story, or solution</li><li>CTA (Next Step)&nbsp;– What you want viewers to do next</li></ul><p><br></p><p>These scripts are frameworks. Customize them with:</p><ul><li>Your personal stories and examples</li><li>Your audience''s specific pain points</li><li>Your brand voice and energy</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Scripts included:</p><ol><li><span style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">I Built an Engineering Portfolio From Scratch (Here''s How)</span></li><li><span style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">Building a Smartwatch From Scratch (Complete Walkthrough)</span></li><li><span style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">Building a Control System From Scratch (Ball &amp; Beam Project)</span></li><li><span style="background-color: oklch(0.9902 0.004 106.47); color: oklch(0.3039 0.04 213.68);">How 2 Projects Got Me 3 Job Offers (My Engineering Story)</span></li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>These scripts are already added to your 30-day calendar. View them here for additional access.</strong></p>', 'file-viewer.html?fileId=92359a29-a8d2-4409-9dfc-799f30dfaef2', 3, '2025-12-28T19:47:03.111Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:03.111Z'),
