('7da0b537-ad82-4bcc-9d8b-dfb74edc2b43', 'b48bc69d-b006-4d9b-96cc-2aeb4b25dc22', '', 'Instagram Execution Assets Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 2: Instagram Execution Assets</h1><p>Instagram is where you build community, trust, and direct relationships with your audience. But it''s also where most creators burn out—posting randomly, chasing trends, and spending hours on their phone.</p><p><br></p><p>This module gives you a&nbsp;plug-and-play system&nbsp;so you can show up consistently without living on the app.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>30-Day Instagram Posting Calendar&nbsp;– Daily post ideas and captions (stored in Compass)</li><li>10 Carousel Post Templates&nbsp;– Fill-in-the-blank designs for high engagement</li><li>15+ Complete Captions&nbsp;– Ready to post or customize</li><li>4-Week Stories Strategy&nbsp;– Daily Story ideas to stay top-of-mind</li><li>Instagram Engagement Playbook&nbsp;– How to turn followers into fans through DMs and comments</li><li>Reel Ideas Guide&nbsp;– High-impact concepts that don''t require dancing</li></ul><h2><br></h2><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You''re posting inconsistently because you don''t know what to say</li><li>You spend hours creating content but get low engagement</li><li>You want to use Stories strategically but don''t have a plan</li><li>You''re overwhelmed by Reels and need simple, effective ideas</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><ul><li>30 days of Instagram content ready to execute</li><li>Templates that make content creation 10x faster</li><li>A Stories strategy that keeps you top-of-mind daily</li><li>An engagement system that builds real relationships</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;2-3 hours to review and customize. Then execute daily for 30 days.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:47:01.827Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:01.827Z'),
