('5dd4df9d-4c9b-491f-8e42-84094d8f344b', '78fdee21-62ca-44f4-8f2f-1ff5b36d3efa', '', 'Sponsorship & Pitch Assets Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 3: Sponsorship &amp; Pitch Assets</h1><p>You''ve built the audience. Now it''s time to get paid for it.</p><p><br></p><p>Sponsorships aren''t about begging brands for money—they''re about offering&nbsp;real business value. This module gives you the professional toolkit to approach brands with confidence, pitch like a pro, and close deals that pay you what you''re worth.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>Complete LinkedIn Outreach Sequence&nbsp;– Connection request → value message → pitch (step-by-step)</li><li>5 Customizable Sponsorship Pitch Templates&nbsp;– Different budget levels and partnership models</li><li>Email + LinkedIn Message Swipe Files&nbsp;– Copy-paste-ready outreach messages</li><li>Sponsorship Agreement Template&nbsp;– Legal protection for every deal</li><li>Sponsor Benefits Package Outline&nbsp;– What you offer at different price points</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You have an audience but don''t know how to monetize through sponsorships</li><li>You''ve reached out to brands but never get responses</li><li>You''ve landed deals but don''t have contracts or pricing clarity</li><li>You want to pitch confidently without feeling salesy</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><ul><li>A proven outreach system that gets responses</li><li>Professional pitch decks for different partnership types</li><li>Legal agreements to protect your work</li><li>Clarity on how to price your sponsorships</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;3-4 hours to customize templates. Then start outreach immediately.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:47:00.791Z', '2025-12-28T19:47:00.791Z'),
