('b2a12752-82be-486f-87d2-09d60b1cbfd8', 'b92c3ad4-1072-404a-be67-5c757174c226', '', 'Community & Partnership Outreach Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 4: Community &amp; Partnership Outreach</h1><p>Online growth is great. But&nbsp;real connection happens in the room.</p><p><br></p><p>This module is your "Event-in-a-Box" for getting in front of real people—campus clubs, local business groups, industry organizations, and community spaces. You''ll walk in with a proven workshop, capture emails like a pro, and turn attendees into lifelong subscribers.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>Complete Club Outreach Email Template&nbsp;– The exact email that gets responses</li><li>Workshop Outline + Speaker Notes (60-Minute Format)&nbsp;– Plug-and-play presentation structure</li><li>Email Capture Strategy&nbsp;– How to get 50%+ of attendees on your list</li><li>Follow-Up Email Sequence&nbsp;– Convert workshop attendees into customers</li><li>Post-Workshop Thank You + Social Proof Request Template&nbsp;– Build testimonials and referrals</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You want to grow offline but don''t know how to approach organizations</li><li>You''ve been invited to speak but don''t have a structured workshop ready</li><li>You''re speaking at events but not capturing emails effectively</li><li>You need a system to convert attendees into customers after the event</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><ul><li>A proven outreach email that books you speaking gigs</li><li>A 60-minute workshop you can deliver confidently</li><li>An email capture strategy that builds your list fast</li><li>A follow-up system that turns attendees into paying customers</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;3-4 hours to customize materials. Then start outreach and book your first event.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:46:59.470Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:59.470Z'),
