('18a265d3-dbd6-4786-a0e2-a4ca9b418b9f', 'e463d643-997a-4175-bc72-70daa806dc78', '', 'Affiliate Marketing System Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 5: Affiliate Marketing System</h1><p>The smartest way to scale?&nbsp;Stop being the only person selling your product.</p><p><br></p><p>This module sets you up to recruit a team of partners who will sell for you. We cover the math (commissions), the method (recruitment), and the management—so you can add a revenue stream without building a whole new product.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>Complete Affiliate Program Guide &nbsp;– Commission structures, pros/cons, tracking systems</li><li>Affiliate Recruitment Email Templates&nbsp;– Proven scripts that get responses</li><li>Affiliate Onboarding Package&nbsp;– Welcome email, onboarding form, and training resources</li><li>Affiliate Tracking + Payment Management Guidance&nbsp;– Tools and systems to manage your program</li><li>10+ Affiliation Pitch Variations&nbsp;– Customized for different creator types</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You have a product or service but struggle to generate consistent sales</li><li>You want to scale revenue without paid ads or creating new products</li><li>You''ve thought about affiliates but don''t know how to structure a program</li><li>You need a system to recruit, onboard, and manage affiliate partners</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><ul><li>A complete affiliate program structure with clear commission rates</li><li>Recruitment emails that attract high-quality partners</li><li>An onboarding system that sets affiliates up for success</li><li>Tools to track performance and pay commissions accurately</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;4-5 hours to build your program structure and customize templates. Then start recruiting.</p><p><br></p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:46:58.327Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:58.327Z'),
