('a11ffd43-ee62-4c47-91a1-d40eb11bfaa9', 'e463d643-997a-4175-bc72-70daa806dc78', '', 'Affiliate Recruitment Email Templates', 'embedded_file', '', 'file-viewer.html?fileId=143d192c-a3a0-4059-a98a-a1ec03d1f77c', 3, '2025-12-28T19:46:57.803Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:57.803Z'),
('f2c6c3cb-7b07-472f-b6cc-50f115dd57d8', 'b0049cc7-76ad-43d9-ad58-3b83a8c96e13', '', 'Welcome to Compass (Your Content Command Center)', 'text', '<h1>Welcome to Compass</h1><p>Compass is your custom content planning platform—where all your calendars, scripts, briefs, and strategies live in one organized system.</p><p><br></p><p>Instead of juggling Google Docs, spreadsheets, and random notes, Compass gives you a single dashboard to plan, schedule, and execute your entire content strategy.</p><h2>What You Can Do in Compass</h2><ul><li>View your 30-day content calendars&nbsp;for YouTube, Instagram, and other platforms</li><li>Access complete content briefs&nbsp;with topics, hooks, captions, and scripts</li><li>Track your progress&nbsp;as you complete tasks</li><li>Customize and edit&nbsp;every piece of content to match your voice</li><li>Export your calendar&nbsp;as a CSV for offline work or batch creation</li><li>Filter by platform&nbsp;to focus on one channel at a time</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Why We Use Compass</h2><p>Most course platforms just give you files to download. But&nbsp;content planning requires action, not just consumption.&nbsp;Compass makes it easy to see what to post, when to post it, and how to execute—all without switching between 10 different tools.</p><p><br></p><p>Think of Compass as your personal content assistant.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:46:57.500Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:57.500Z'),
('57c750e4-8bb7-47f4-9733-e86a69c65cc2', 'b0049cc7-76ad-43d9-ad58-3b83a8c96e13', '', 'Interactive Compass Tutorial', 'video', '', 'https://app.supademo.com/demo/cmjp3jtoa5yg13zz2eza2p0of?utm_source=link', 2, '2025-12-28T19:46:57.237Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:57.237Z'),
('f96fd287-15a0-406f-90c3-77af66dc259a', 'b0049cc7-76ad-43d9-ad58-3b83a8c96e13', '', 'Compass Quick Start Guide', 'text', '<h2>Step 1: Log Into Compass</h2><p>Your login details were sent to your email.&nbsp;If you can''t find them, check your spam folder or email [support email].</p><p><br></p><p>Login URL:&nbsp;https://kaylasierra.com/compass -&gt; works on mobile and on the web!</p><p><br></p><h2>Step 2: Navigate to Your Content Calendar</h2><p>Once logged in, you''ll see your dashboard.</p><p>To access your content calendar:</p><ol><li>Click&nbsp;"Content Calendar"&nbsp;in the left sidebar</li><li>Your full calendar view will load showing all platforms</li></ol><p><br></p><h2>Step 3: Filter by Platform</h2><p>You''ll see content for YouTube, Instagram, LinkedIn, and more all in one view. To focus on one platform:</p><ol><li>Look for the&nbsp;"Filter"&nbsp;dropdown at the top of the calendar</li><li>Select&nbsp;"YouTube"&nbsp;or&nbsp;"Instagram"&nbsp;(or whichever platform you''re working on)</li><li>The calendar will update to show only that platform''s content</li></ol><p><br></p><h2>Step 4: Open a Content Brief</h2><p>Each day on your calendar is clickable. To see the full content brief:</p><ol><li>Click on any day&nbsp;in your calendar</li><li>A side panel will open showing:</li></ol><ul><li class="ql-indent-1">Topic/Title&nbsp;for that day''s content</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Hook ideas&nbsp;to grab attention</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Complete caption or script&nbsp;(ready to customize)</li><li class="ql-indent-1">SEO keywords&nbsp;(for YouTube)</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Suggested posting time</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Content format&nbsp;(carousel, reel, video, etc.)</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Step 5: Customize Your Content</h2><p>Don''t just copy-paste.&nbsp;These are frameworks designed to be customized.</p><p>To edit content:</p><ol><li>Click the&nbsp;"Edit"&nbsp;button in the content brief</li><li>Replace placeholders with your personal stories, examples, and voice</li><li>Click&nbsp;"Save"&nbsp;when done</li></ol><p><br></p><p>Your changes are saved automatically.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2>Step 6: Mark Tasks as Complete</h2><p>As you post content, mark it complete so you can track your progress.</p><p>To mark complete:</p><ol><li>Open the content brief for that day</li><li>Click the&nbsp;checkbox&nbsp;or&nbsp;"Mark Complete"&nbsp;button</li><li>The task will turn green and move to your "Completed" section</li></ol><p><br></p><h2>Step 7: Export Your Calendar (Optional)</h2><p>Want to work offline or batch-create content? Export your calendar as a CSV.</p><p>To export:</p><ol><li>Click the&nbsp;"Export"&nbsp;button at the top of your calendar</li><li>Choose your calendar service</li><li>Instantly add posting times directly to your calendar</li></ol><p><br></p><h2>Step 8: Access Your Scripts and Templates</h2><p>Some content (like YouTube video scripts or Instagram carousel templates) are stored in separate folders.</p><p>To access:</p><ol><li>Look for the&nbsp;"Assets"&nbsp;or&nbsp;"Templates"&nbsp;tab in the left sidebar</li><li>Browse by content type (Scripts, Carousels, Email Templates, etc.)</li><li>Download or view directly in Compass</li></ol><p><br></p><p>Need help?&nbsp;Email kayla@kaylasierra.com or reference the interactive tutorial in Block 2.</p>', '', 3, '2025-12-28T19:46:56.977Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:56.977Z'),
('32a6370d-ee91-483f-af34-9c61eed0e4f8', '9ffbb0cc-0477-43c0-a932-33963a6751cd', '', 'Strategy & Operations Hub Overview', 'text', '<h1>Module 7: Strategy &amp; Operations Hub</h1><p>This is your&nbsp;CEO toolkit. Strategy isn''t about doing more—it''s about doing the right things in the right order.</p><p><br></p><p>This module gives you the frameworks to make decisions faster, track your progress without obsession, and handle the operational side of scaling without losing your mind.</p><p><br></p><h2>What''s Inside This Module</h2><ul><li>30-Day Implementation Timeline&nbsp;– Your exact day-by-day roadmap (with time estimates)</li><li>Weekly Progress Tracker (in Compass)&nbsp;– Track execution without spreadsheet hell</li><li>Monthly Content Planner (in Compass)&nbsp;– Plan your content strategy month-by-month</li><li>Decision-Making Framework&nbsp;– When to pivot, when to push, when to scale</li><li>FAQ &amp; Troubleshooting Guide – Solutions to 50+ common problems</li><li>Email Copy &amp; Sequences&nbsp;– For nurturing your growing email list</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Who This Module Is For</h2><ul><li>You''re executing but don''t know if you''re prioritizing the right things</li><li>You feel overwhelmed by all the moving pieces</li><li>You''re making decisions based on emotions instead of data</li><li>You need a system to track progress without burning out</li></ul><p><br></p><h2>Expected Outcome</h2><p>By the end of this module, you''ll have:</p><ul><li>A clear 30-day plan with daily priorities</li><li>A tracking system to monitor progress in Compass</li><li>Decision-making frameworks to eliminate guesswork</li><li>Solutions to the most common roadblocks</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Time to complete:&nbsp;2-3 hours to review and set up your systems. Then execute daily.</p>', '', 1, '2025-12-28T19:46:56.717Z', '2025-12-28T19:46:56.717Z'),
